{"tid":2023204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「淪為政治打手」律政司認同連儂牆斬人案兇手有高尚情操，決定不就刑期上訴","createTime":"2020-05-19T00:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T00:50:47.000Z","uid":230104,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e5c5938a7bf48c404a9af3bdc149dee9bb1998b2","tid":2023204,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T00:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ymYSoeH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FymYSoeH.png&h=a92bd315&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b69de36ea44510874315fb3ad981d4a327e6d4f","tid":2023204,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T00:18:11.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】上月廿四日惹起全城譁然的將軍澳連儂隧道斬人案，律政司昨決定，不會就被法官形容為「情操高尚」的被告洪震三年九個月的刑期提覆核。律政司認為，考慮案中所有情況及《檢控守則》後，認為沒有足夠法律基礎支持有關刑罰是明顯不足或有原則上錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n被告洪震（51歲，圖）早前承認去年8月20日凌晨時分帶兩刀，在將軍澳景林邨與頌明苑之間的行人隧道內，非法及惡意傷害兩女一男，當中包括一名肺部重創、一度命危的女記者。法官郭偉健以六年為量刑起點，基於被告認罪，扣減三分一。郭官指被告犯案源自社會事件，相信他真誠後悔、願意承擔責任，表現出高尚情操。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20200519&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20920615\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200519%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20920615&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=c66a48cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200519%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20920615&h=ebe46008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20200519&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20920615</a>"},{"pid":"ba9ceea45d38403fda9b71d229f2e3047a0d1af7","tid":2023204,"uid":188805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T00:25:05.000Z","msg":"Over my dead body<br />\n全力開打國際戰線"},{"pid":"e527d219023797b05f436158cceb8c1567f63130","tid":2023204,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T00:31:46.000Z","msg":"有冇負責單Case律政屍個名？"},{"pid":"ee89c8061